<i>adverb</i>: 진정 [진정], 바른대로 [바른대로], 똑바로 [똑빠로] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진정 [진정]</dt><br>
<dd>sincerely; truthfully</dd><br>
<dd>거짓이 없이 진심으로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a sincere manner without falsehood.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>바른대로 [바른대로]</dt><br>
<dd>right; truthfully; correctly</dd><br>
<dd>사실 그대로.</dd><br>
<dd>Just as it is.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>똑바로 [똑빠로]</dt><br>
<dd>1. straight; upright</dd><br>
<dd>어느 쪽으로도 기울지 않고 곧게.</dd><br>
<dd>Straight, not tilting to any side.</dd><br>
<dd>2. truthfully; honestly</dd><br>
<dd>틀리거나 거짓된 것 없이 사실 그대로.</dd><br>
<dd>As it is without falsity or fabrication.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>